around this experience, and in

00:38:02.896 --> 00:38:04.686 A:middle
doing so, we've lifted a huge

00:38:04.686 --> 00:38:06.036 A:middle
cognitive burden off the user.

00:38:06.636 --> 00:38:08.256 A:middle
Your users will love this extra

00:38:08.256 --> 00:38:09.496 A:middle
bit of effort you put towards

00:38:09.496 --> 00:38:11.226 A:middle
the accessibility of the app so

00:38:11.226 --> 00:38:12.196 A:middle
they can love it as much as

00:38:12.196 --> 00:38:12.786 A:middle
