I'd like to hand it back to

00:38:14.076 --> 00:38:16.436 A:middle
Skyler now.

00:38:17.516 --> 00:38:19.876 A:middle
[ Applause ]

00:38:20.376 --> 00:38:21.956 A:middle
&gt;&gt; Thanks, Bhavya.

00:38:22.836 --> 00:38:23.826 A:middle
Hopefully Bhavya's demo

00:38:23.826 --> 00:38:25.756 A:middle
demonstrated for you how small

00:38:25.756 --> 00:38:27.106 A:middle
