00:38:29.786 --> 00:38:30.866 A:middle
It's important to note that

00:38:30.866 --> 00:38:32.796 A:middle
creating custom interfaces for

00:38:32.796 --> 00:38:34.176 A:middle
the accessibility of your app is

00:38:34.176 --> 00:38:35.836 A:middle
not always the right answer.

00:38:36.456 --> 00:38:38.266 A:middle
Sometimes the simple fix is the

00:38:38.266 --> 00:38:40.996 A:middle
best fix, but what you really

00:38:40.996 --> 00:38:42.436 A:middle
should be doing when making your

00:38:42.436 --> 00:38:44.716 A:middle
apps accessible is thinking

00:38:44.716 --> 00:38:46.376 A:middle
through beyond the surface level

00:38:46.376 --> 00:38:47.856 A:middle
what it will really mean for

00:38:47.856 --> 00:38:49.486 A:middle
someone who's using an assistive

00:38:49.486 --> 00:38:53.036 A:middle
technology to use your app.

